title: Destiny's Two
subTitle: A man newly married to a dwarf decides to go to a red-light area to fulfill his desire for a taller woman.

title: Girl in Red
subTitle: A writer who is struggling with writer's block is in search of a story. However, he lands himself in trouble when he stumbles upon a deadly secret while talking to his garbage collector.

title: Harmless
subTitle: A boy in need of money to make it big in life and a girl who is looking for thrill concoct a plan and stage a kidnapping to extort money from the girl's rich father.

title: Exchange Offer
subTitle: Shiv lives alone, writing poetry on an old computer that breaks down. However, a service visit arranged by his son brings unexpected nostalgia, surprises and an intriguing exchange offer.

title: Loha Chor
subTitle: A family moves in from Delhi to a house that was previously tenanted by an iron thief. Furthermore, chaos ensues when the police investigates their residence.

title: Black Coffee
subTitle: A woman faces sexual harassment at the hands of her boss. Later, she decides to teach him a lesson with the help of her colleague.

title: Ansh: The Deadly Part
subTitle: An honest police officer dedicated to uprooting crime ruffles the feathers of corrupt politicians and criminals, who scheme to stop him.

title: Ahsaas
subTitle: After being rejected by their fathers, Raju and Anu elope and get settled in a village but when the parents learn about their whereabouts, they decide to bring them back.

title: Woh Khaas
subTitle: A successful businessman decides to take a break from his mundane life and goes on a vacation. Furthermore, he happens to meet a stranger who transforms him.

title: Raah
subTitle: Raahis an exploration of the several stages of struggle when one steps out to pursue a dream. Sahir lives in Mumbai city with his family. The emotional and poetic narrative explores his faith, kinship and his struggle to establish himself.

title: Uyire Uyire
subTitle: Rahul and Priya meet during a trip to Goa and fall in love with each other. However, their lives take a turn when Rahul learns that Priya is the sibling of Shiva, who had once tortured his sister.

title: Wazir
subTitle: When his daughter is killed by the terrorist he is chasing, Daanish, a policeman, vows revenge. He finds a confidante in Pandit, a grandmaster, who is also mourning the loss of his daughter.

title: #Goals
subTitle: After some time apart, Meera and Ranbir find their relationship at a point where it becomes a perfect example of the shallowness and fragility of modern-day dating.

title: A Tale Of An Onion Witch Chapter 2
Half Cake
subTitle: A poor single mother goes through life struggling her way to earn extra wages to complete her child's desire to have a cake.

title: Harshit
subTitle: Fate plays a twisted game with Harshit and Rahila, who are madly in love with each other.

title: Dum Dum Deega Deega
subTitle: Ajju, the son of a drunkard beggar, lives on the streets of Mumbai but holds a positive outlook towards life. He refuses to beg and tries to earn money through respectable means.
